{"tid":1417096,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民間記者會  策略討論POST (1st Round - 8月6日 11:00)","createTime":"2019-08-05T16:00:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T05:23:17.000Z","uid":54684,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"6852da50797e260e556984d15c1aff3794d1fba9","tid":1417096,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:00:14.000Z","msg":"見到有人搞民間記者會，但上個post爆左，<br />\n我認為呢場係一場<strong>大文宣</strong>，應該深入討論，應該愈做愈pro<br />\n<br />\n<em>8月6  11：00<br />\n會有第一次民間記者會<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1414615\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1414615</a></em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家不妨繼續brainstorm下idea   等件事愈做愈好<br />\n我講下有咩ideas先<br />\n<br />\n<strong>時間</strong><br />\n- 最好下次係AFTER警察既記招，每次都食住人來講<br />\n- 揀最最最多人睇住電視既時候，例如8 pm-10 pm<br />\n<br />\n<strong>主講人士</strong><br />\n要有公信力，場面夠formal<br />\n主持人予人立場不太深黃，可以係人權組織大佬<br />\n英文能力要好，一定要比警察好得多<br />\n亦可以有一個專業English speaker陪住main speaker<br />\n<br />\n<strong>話題︰</strong><br />\n&gt;&gt; 針對警方的指控，及犯下的錯誤<br />\n- 違返大量警例 (委任證，擅闖民居，遮number，公開信...)<br />\n- 警黑合作問題<br />\n- 白衣人非法集結，黑衣人暴動罪<br />\n- 民居中射彈<br />\n- 有少女被性侵，嚴重違犯人權<br />\n- 政府高層只用警力擋而不作為<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n<strong>展示證據 (Evidence)</strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">例子︰7.28 香港上環</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y15Cr4H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy15Cr4H.png&h=0ecce7b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n戴紅十字頭盔都打<br />\nPersonnels in red cross helmets were also beaten up. <br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1377029/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1377029/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oCZDbwx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoCZDbwx.jpg&h=01085a16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n22:30 警方登上停車場狙擊樓下 <br />\nAt 22:30, policemen went up to a carpark building nearby to fire shots towards the protesters on the street below. <br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1377765/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1377765/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jwpzuiv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJwpzuiv.png&h=ce7281c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小朋友亦被催淚煙傷到<br />\nEven children were attacked by the police using tear gas canisters. <br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1377350/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1377350/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LBgRwwZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLBgRwwZ.png&h=a617c06b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前線鋼板都射穿埋<br />\nLethal shots which can cause a hole on metal shields were fired by the police. <br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1377493/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1377493/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7nZDbxk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7nZDbxk.gif&h=a557dc67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黑警對被捕者動私刑<br />\nA band of policemen was caught on camera when repeatedly abusing and attacking a man's head who was already subdued. <br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1378018/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1378018/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n黑警以燃燒彈攻擊記者<br />\nA policeman was caught on camera when throwing a firebomb to reporters nearby. <br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkon9agroup/permalink/2979309865443391?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkon9agroup%2Fpermalink%2F2979309865443391%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=aRHHWgZm4a4JNL46Iov0BHf7N2ZoUQ5IAXdO3fO0pAc%3D&h=53309b17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkon9agroup/permalink/2979309865443391?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>器材︰</strong><br />\n預先係身後準備screen/monitor，播放預先準備既evidence/movie clip<br />\n你當powerpoint咁整都得，咁就可以加埋annotation (箭咀指住/圈住重點，例如跪下既外國人係邊度？何君堯係邊度？)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">- 減少政治口號，主力指責政府打記者 / 欺淩市民 / 疑有明顯黑社會勾結問題，令大眾信服，每個位都有EVIDENCE，都解釋清楚，都係佢犯錯</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n諗到再講[/quote]"},{"pid":"8bca4360873146893e30a5d94bfc7bf4582cae39","tid":1417096,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:01:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d2f23bd3f8cade93fd700d98fb5b8155dca494c","tid":1417096,"uid":154486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:03:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">重點<br />\n差佬換黑衫<br />\n有可能係自己放火嫁禍義士<br />\n</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"ce907e21ec5072ad31fe9d0797bc9df905b0ef54","tid":1417096,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:03:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae990139979c3877c5fd9f4265f2469f2a045f13","tid":1417096,"uid":81151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:03:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"44537b12419663e62da8cdb85204a19be3a813f7","tid":1417096,"uid":171718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:05:00.000Z","msg":"最重要係引evidence因為唔知影片來源擁有者比唔比播 eg. Nowtv, rthk, etc"},{"pid":"e2cf8d0ab0a654c58bdbf0961f76c59d3959a040","tid":1417096,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:08:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69ff699c53edcd4c7c6b101ae0b5fcc960611263","tid":1417096,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:12:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"529c85f8993f1550c2148c649b077e29d0